Thank you for downloading CMDSecure for Linux. 
Lets get started! 

1. In order to install CMDSecure for Linux please go to the install directory under CMDSecure for linux. The file path should look like the following:
 /cmdsecure_linux/install/

2.Once you are in that directory in terminal type the following
    sudo chmod u+x install

followed by

    ./install

3. You will recieve a conformation message that CMDSecure for Linux has been installed



